''Another Language'' received positive reviews upon its release. According to [[Metacritic]], which assigns a normalized rating out of 100 to reviews from mainstream critics, the album held a score of 78/100 based on four reviews<U+2014>indicating "generally favorable reviews"<U+2014>following its release.<ref name=metacritic/>

